quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  26,105,Qaum e Nooh ne Rasoolon ko jhutlaya
  26,106,Yaad karo jabke unke bhai Nooh ne unsey kaha tha “kya tum darte nahin ho
  26,107,Main tumhare liye ek amaanat daar Rasool hoon
  26,108,Lihaza tum Allah se daro aur meri itaat karo
  26,109,"Main is kaam par tumse kisi ajar ka talib nahin hoon, mera ajar to Rabbul Aalameen ke zimme hai"
  26,110,Pas tum Allah se daro aur ( be khatke) meri itaat karo”
  26,111,Unhon ne jawab diya “kya hum tujhey maan lein halaanke teri pairwi razil-tareen (lowest/meanest) logon ne ikhtiyar ki hai?”
  26,112,Nooh ne kaha “main kya jaanu ke unke amal kaise hain
  26,113,"Unka hisaab to mere Rubb ke zimme hai, kaash tum kuch shaoor se kaam lo"
  26,114,Mera yeh kaam nahin hai ke jo iman layein unko main dhutkaar doon
  26,115,Main to bas ek saaf saaf mutanabbeh (warn) kardene wala aadmi hoon”
  26,116,"Unhon ne kaha “Aey Nooh , agar tu baaz na aaya to phitkarey huey logon mein shamil hokar rahega”"
  26,117,"Nooh ne dua ki “Aey mere Rubb, meri qaum ne mujhey jhutla diya"
  26,118,Ab mere aur unke darmiyan do-toak faisla karde aur mujhey aur jo momin mere saath hain inko nijaat de”
  26,119,Aakhir e kaar humne usko aur uske saathiyon ko ek bhaari hui kashti mein bacha liya
  26,120,Aur uske baad baaqi logon ko garq (drown) kardiya
  26,121,"Yaqeenan ismein ek nishani hai, magar inmein se aksar log maanne waley nahin"
  26,122,Aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera Rubb zabardast bhi hai aur raheem bhi